definitions.definition: A market town with a town council in North Northamptonshire district, Northamptonshire , England ( OS grid ref SP8967 ) .
A former borough in Northamptonshire , formed in 1974, with its headquarters in the town, abolished 1 April 2021 and merged into North Northamptonshire .
